|============================
| Service: Texture Generator
|============================
- Build Image 50x50
- Extract random frag from pool of images
- Use GD to darken and derive "space" from "block"
- return "space" + "block"

===========================
| Texture Maker
===========================

- Expect input_glob constructor arg
- Create config 'textures.php' with input_glob => '...'
- Create a bind on service provider passing config('textures.input_glob')

============================
| Room Factory:
============================

- Create Random Room
- Room Method spawnWarpTo(Room2)
- Room Method getAvailablePositions()
- Select a Random Room (if exists) (prefer rooms without warps) and Link Through Location / Warp
- Create method Room->findAvailablePositions() [x,y] [x,y] etc...

===============================
| /rooms (auth)
================================
- Name | Thumbnail | [Teleport] (todo: teleport will cost money/points later)

===========================
| /rooms/{room} (auth)
===========================
- If user is not located -> redirect /rooms
- If user is not in this room -> show error / redirect
- Otherwise: show room at current position
- Allow click on spaces to move

===========================
| /rooms/{room}/move (auth)
===========================
- Grab x, y -> realocate user
- redirect to /rooms/{id}

